manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: VECELO Upholstered Platform Bed Frame with Linen Fabric Headboard Less is more - This smooth, minimalist, and stylish platform bed frame replaces basic metal bed frames and box springs, using fabric padding and wooden slats to provide reliable yet understated support. No Box Spring Needed - Durable wooden slats can support latex, memory foam, or innerspring mattresses and extend their lifespan without a box spring.

Velcro Design: Easier Installation, No Noise when sleeping turn over. Thick Wooden Slats: The 12 bed slats are made of solid wood and provide strong support for you and your mattress. Strong and durable, not easy to bend.

It provides a comfortable sleeping space, giving you a sense of care and security. Lean in Comfort Ergonomic design. When watching TV or reading books, leaning against the headboard is comfortable, relaxing, and helps relieve the fatigue from the entire day.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Affordable, Luxury-looking Queen Bed Frame
reviews.reviewText: Wow, I am honestly amazed at the quality of this bed frame for the price. I originally was looking for just a box spring, but came across this affordable queen bed that didn't require a box spring. It looks 100x better than what I even anticipated. The adjustable headboard was a great feature especially for the sloped ceilings in my cape cod style home. The material is beautiful and almost looks to be a textured linen.This bed frame took me about 45 minutes to put together on my own. I was even able to carry the box in the house myself. It is so sturdy, and stable. It didnt move around with my mattress on it at all. It worked great with my older mattress with a memory foam topper. The frame is constructed with durable materials, including steel and wood slats. The velcro bed slats were perfect and so easy to assemble.Also, I am so pleased with the under-bed storage space, which is perfect for my smaller room to help with organization.Overall, this Vecelo queen bed frame is top-notch for the price. It is such a great deal at less than $160ish. I would have spent so much more at a furniture store. I understand individual experiences can be different, but for me, I am so pleased!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Overall I am very pleased with this bed, however 2 main things may throw others off:1) The color on the listing on my monitor for the blue bed is very blue, like a royal blue. The bed's upholstery in person is much greener, more like a dark teal.2) The fabric stinks. This is common for fabric coming straight out of the factory, which means the fabric probably wasn't washed prior to being applied to the frame. If I did it over I would open the box, take all of the pieces with fabric out and put them in a well ventilated place for a few days to get the stink off. Be very cautious when cleaning, spot test it first, as there is no telling how color fast the dye is.Overall I like this bed. Assembly is not too complicated, the instructions required a bit of puzzling a couple of times but nothing outrageous. I applied a lubricant to any metal-on-metal joins and tightened them down firmly at the end to help prevent future squeaking.
